             person(family = "WavX Inc.", role = "cph"))
Maintainer: Jean Marchal <jean.marchal@wavx.ca>
Description: The bioacoustics package contains all the necessary tools to process
    audio recordings of various formats (e.g., WAV, WAC, MP3, ZC), filter noisy
    files, display audio signals, detect and extract automatically acoustic
    features for further analysis such as classification.
